1
00:00:12,320 --> 00:00:17,839
That night…
I kissed hyung.

2
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
After that, he acted
like nothing ever happened.

3
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,175
Is he pretending he doesn’t know?
Or…

4
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:34,320
does he think it was just a mistake?

5
00:00:35,480 --> 00:00:41,800
This year,
I wanted to go see the cherry blossoms with him.

6
00:00:43,160 --> 00:00:47,920
But I think… I’m too late.

7
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,527
He’s so handsome.

8
00:01:03,527 --> 00:01:04,949
Who is he?

9
00:01:04,949 --> 00:01:10,167
That new business freshman—
he’s seriously gorgeous.

10
00:01:14,759 --> 00:01:15,987
Yes, hello?

11
00:01:15,987 --> 00:01:21,600
Is this Mr. Seo Yujin?
This is Lime Agency.
We offered you a casting call in front of your school before—

12
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:23,647
do you remember?

13
00:01:23,647 --> 00:01:25,404
Oh… yes.

14
00:01:25,404 --> 00:01:34,577
We have a short-term lookbook project,
and we think your image would be a great fit.
It’s a one-day shoot, and the pay is quite good.

15
00:01:41,079 --> 00:01:44,581
Ah…
I’ll do it. When is the shoot?

16
00:01:45,198 --> 00:01:50,000
For hyung’s birthday this year,
I can get him something better.

17
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:12,407
You said you wouldn’t contact me again.

18
00:02:13,635 --> 00:02:17,187
Sorry, but I have nothing to say.

19
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,767
Yujin, welcome.

20
00:02:43,279 --> 00:02:44,525
Hi. Hello.

21
00:02:44,525 --> 00:02:53,620
Like I mentioned at our last meeting,
today we’re shooting a denim concept—
natural, not overly styled.

22
00:02:57,879 --> 00:03:01,785
You said you’re twenty, right?
Your skin is amazing.

23
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:10,400
But your complexion is very fair,
so under the lights it might look a bit washed out.

24
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:13,937
Hmm. I’ll just even out the tone a little—on your body too.

25
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:24,080
It’ll look better if you don’t button it up—
just wear it naturally.

26
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,350
Great. Just relax.

27
00:03:26,457 --> 00:03:28,164
Nice. This shot is good.

28
00:03:28,483 --> 00:03:32,037
Don’t force an expression—just look.
That’s better. Good. Hold it…

29
00:03:32,251 --> 00:03:34,267
Oh, nice. It suits you way more than I expected.

30
00:03:35,311 --> 00:03:36,647
Looks good.

31
00:03:38,906 --> 00:03:41,140
Great. Stay like that.

32
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:56,830
Yujin, you did great today.
It turned out even better than I thought.

33
00:03:58,599 --> 00:04:03,788
If you take this seriously, I think you’d do really well.
Have you ever thought about continuing?

34
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:05,481
Ah…

35
00:04:05,928 --> 00:04:07,857
I’ll think about it.

36
00:04:11,799 --> 00:04:16,661
No pressure.
If you ever become interested, call me anytime.

37
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:43,039
That’s his ex-girlfriend, right?
Getting back together…

38
00:04:43,039 --> 00:04:44,718
No way.

39
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:25,344
Oh my gosh—boss, isn’t this Yujin?

40
00:05:25,919 --> 00:05:28,135
Look at this.

41
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:31,328
What… is this?

42
00:05:31,435 --> 00:05:33,716
Who is he?/This vibe is insane./That body line—wow./Is he like that in real life?

43
00:05:34,204 --> 00:05:39,286
That’s you, right? Wow—you look amazing.
You look like a model. Seriously.

44
00:05:40,939 --> 00:05:42,472
When did you do something like this…?

45
00:05:43,197 --> 00:05:47,414
The comments are blowing up too.
Isn’t this basically going viral?

46
00:05:50,639 --> 00:05:52,105
Really?

47
00:05:53,592 --> 00:05:55,744
I should get to work.

48
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,694
Are you waiting for someone to text you or what?

49
00:06:31,163 --> 00:06:33,545
No, not really.

50
00:06:34,888 --> 00:06:39,161
By the way—
what is this? That’s you, right?

51
00:06:43,998 --> 00:06:45,742
Why is it posted here?

52
00:06:46,402 --> 00:06:52,138
How famous are you trying to get?
You look skinny, but those abs were no joke.

53
00:06:54,311 --> 00:06:56,964
It’s just the lighting.

54
00:06:58,946 --> 00:07:02,111
Lighting, my ass. The comments went crazy.

55
00:07:03,475 --> 00:07:07,114
Wait—no way. It really is you?

56
00:07:07,114 --> 00:07:09,913
You’re that new business freshman, right?

57
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:26,039
Hey, you were seriously the talk of the day.
So listen—

58
00:07:26,039 --> 00:07:28,369
can you come to a meeting with me today?

59
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:33,059
Seriously, I really want to bring you this time.

60
00:07:33,059 --> 00:07:35,157
Can’t you just show your face once?

61
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:40,421
I told you there’s someone I like.

62
00:07:40,421 --> 00:07:46,233
What does that have to do with going to a meeting?

63
00:07:46,233 --> 00:07:52,958
I’m genuinely curious.
What kind of girl would ever turn you down?

64
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:57,910
I have somewhere I need to go today.

65
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:02,205
Seriously, you’re so weird.

66
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:19,607
Is it for a gift?

67
00:08:19,692 --> 00:08:20,521
Yes.

68
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:25,264
What kind of style does the recipient have?

69
00:08:25,499 --> 00:08:29,099
Calm… and gentle.

70
00:08:29,483 --> 00:08:32,641
This scent is soft and clean,
so it’s a popular choice for gifts.

71
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:44,836
Mm…
I’ll look around a bit more.

72
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:07,418
This model is a popular gift choice.
It’s clean and easy to use for a long time,

73
00:09:07,418 --> 00:09:10,475
and it’s one of the safest picks for men.

74
00:09:16,279 --> 00:09:17,967
This…

75
00:09:18,713 --> 00:09:20,492
Please wrap it.

76
00:09:20,492 --> 00:09:23,541
Of course. I’ll help you with gift packaging.

77
00:09:54,865 --> 00:09:57,268
Hyung, are you free on the 5th?

78
00:09:58,121 --> 00:10:01,582
It’s your birthday…
I wanted to celebrate with you.

79
00:10:12,108 --> 00:10:13,788
Yeah. Thanks.

80
00:10:13,788 --> 00:10:15,511
Can you come when the café closes?

81
00:10:19,432 --> 00:10:23,169
Yeah. I’ll come right at closing time.

82
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:33,381
That day…

83
00:10:33,381 --> 00:10:35,642
Will I be able to say it?
